headline: How The LKQ (LKQ) Story Is Shifting As Analysts Rework Targets After Q4
summary: The updated analyst work on LKQ centers on a modest move in the price target to US$34, paired with a refreshed model fair value of US$40.69, down slightly from US$41.19. Analysts link this smaller adjustment to their read of the Q4 report, suggesting that, while their stance remains measured, they see enough support in the latest numbers to fine tune rather than overhaul their view.
